Privacy Policy
Kagi's Orion Browser is commited to respecting your privacy.
We do not collect any usage or other telemetry data by default.
You may volunteer to us your email address to join the waitlist, in
        which case it will be used to contact you with the invite.
You may volunteer to send us Orion browser crash report in which case
        you will have control of data being sent.
In case you enable automatic updates, Orion will check for updates
      at start and offer you to download the latest version.
In case of interaction with Orion servers, no information
      is sent to Orion other than current browser version, and your IP
      address is not logged.
